OL,5, The debt mountain at UK councils has   
OL,6, reached staggering levels, posing a    
OL,7, risk to local services, the Public     
OL,8, Accounts Committee has said.           
OL,10,FBBC analysis shows UK councils owe a   
OL,11,Fcombined #97.8bn to lenders, equivalent
OL,12,Fto around #1,400 per person.           
OL,14,FCommittee chair Meg Hillier warned of  
OL,15,Fan "extreme and long-lasting effect" if
OL,16,Fmore councils go bust.                 
OL,18,FCouncil leaders say years of government
OL,19,Funder-funding have forced them to      
OL,20,Finvest in commercial ventures.         
